We took them out fairly easy but with the cleric down to 1m after each one. The other mobs on the floor will not aggro through the doors, so your only concern are pats  in the hallway. The mobs wearing the robes dispell so I would suggest you crap buff before attacking those. I would also suggest that you have a full standard group for these as to reduce downtime and to be prepared for any adds.<br>
